{"tid":33183,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"解放軍多架軍機  順時鐘繞台飛行","createTime":"2016-12-10T15:53:02.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-11T03:12:11.000Z","uid":30743,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a8d5bc24b6f61c3a1acaecb2d00fdba5aeaa9026","tid":33183,"uid":30743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T15:53:02.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】大陸多架解放軍軍機在台灣南部的防空識別區外圍繞飛行，期間軍機經過宮古海峽時，日本自衛隊出動兩架戰機升空，並發射干擾彈。<br />\n<br />\n台灣的國防部表示，有十多架參與遠海訓練的解放軍軍機，在星期六早上九時起，從東部戰區升空，由北向南穿越宮古水道。其中有四架軍機，包括電子偵察機，穿越巴士海峽，並由南部戰區的殲擊機掩護下，在台灣南部防空識別區外，沿着巴士海峽繞台一周。一時許結束訓練。<br />\n<br />\n台灣當局在大陸軍機返航後十分鐘，隨即發表公布，表示全程嚴密監控。<br />\n<br />\n值得關注是，以往類似的消息，也是日本防衛省率先發布，今次是台灣主動公布。<br />\n<br />\n同時，今次是繼上月25日後，解放軍軍機第二次圍繞台灣飛行。上次是逆時鐘方向，而今次是順時鐘方向。"},{"pid":"a1672c007fa58803bca1cb85555771f654082dbd","tid":33183,"uid":30743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T15:53:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=203383\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D203383&d=ZM0jouo7Vlg%2BeAAmEV3FLWN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=d51cd387\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D203383&h=71a505da\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=203383</a>"},{"pid":"395928c6e2e7d9d6e6229940aca8dae5b92fa582","tid":33183,"uid":48582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T15:53:52.000Z","msg":"WFC<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0fff33a3cb6a0f608479b0c9d102ff272c8cd44","tid":33183,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T15:56:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8597ae2ec4e9aca0f5746dec786d4aaa9e4449cd","tid":33183,"uid":49784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T02:59:46.000Z","msg":"中國打始聊仗打"},{"pid":"f39687c3f8df485cba1dabab3892561e7eacd5e7","tid":33183,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T03:12:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中國打始聊仗打</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n開始了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}